        <text>
            <body>
                
                                        <p>Ego <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324577" xml:id="d1e139943" corresp="Hugues III, duc de Bourgogne (1162-1192)">Hugo, dux <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325098" xml:id="d1e139945" corresp="Bourgogne">Burgundie</placeName>
                        </persName>, scripto presenti notifico presentibus et futuris quod <persName key="d1e14372" xml:id="d1e139948">Matheus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324448" xml:id="d1e139950" corresp="Étais (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                                <foreign>Estez</foreign>
                            </placeName>
                        </persName>
                        <lb n="2" /> dedit et concessit ecclesie Fonteneti in elemosinam terram super
                        abbatiam que dicitur <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325280" xml:id="d1e139955" corresp="Foresta">Foresta</placeName>, in qua <persName key="d1e14378" xml:id="d1e139958">Matheus</persName> habe<lb n="3" break="no" />bat duas partes et monachi
                        terciam, et terram de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324924" xml:id="d1e139964" corresp="Juvance">
                            <foreign>Juvence</foreign>
                        </placeName>, que dicitur <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325281" xml:id="d1e139968" corresp="Foresta sancti Petri">Foresta sancti Petri</placeName>. Pro his duabus duo solidi cen<lb n="4" break="no" />suales in marcio reddendi sunt majori de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324448" xml:id="d1e139973" corresp="Étais (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                            <foreign>Estez</foreign>
                        </placeName>. Dedit etiam hisdem fratribus quantum sui juris erat ad omnia
                            <lb n="5" /> animalia sua usagium in pasturis et pastionem porcis in
                        finagiis duarum villarum, scilicet de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324348" xml:id="d1e139979" corresp="Puits (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Puteis</placeName>
                        <surplus>
                            <del rend="barré">et de <lb n="6" />Puteis</del>
                        </surplus> et de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324448" xml:id="d1e139988" corresp="Étais (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                            <foreign>Estez</foreign>
                        </placeName>, quas pasturas et pastiones de <persName key="d1e14384" xml:id="d1e139992">Rogerio, patre <persName key="d1e14390" xml:id="d1e139994">Mathei</persName>
                        </persName>, habebant in vagio pro quingentis solidis et <lb n="7" />
                        graantavit <persName key="d1e14397" xml:id="d1e139999">Matheus</persName>
                        quod de his omnibus legitimam garentiam pro posse suo portabit sicut debebit
                        et tali quidem conditione <lb n="8" /> utentur <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e140005" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetenses</orgName> predictis pasturis et
                        pastionibus omni tempore quod si animalia eorum aliquod damnum in pratis vel
                            bla<lb n="9" break="no" />dis fecerint, damnum solummodo restituent sine
                        alia emendatione. Si usque ad festum Omnium sanctorum in pratis <lb n="10" />
                        fena remanserint et animalia monachorum ibi damnum fecerint, damnum
                        solummodo sine alia lege restituetur. Si post <lb n="11" /> festum Omnium
                        sanctorum de fenis damnum factum fuerit, nichil inde <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e140014" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetenses</orgName> reddent.
                        Et sciendum quod Fontene<lb n="12" break="no" />tenses nulla animalia nisi
                        sua in easdem pasturas et pastiones adducent, nec <persName key="d1e14403" xml:id="d1e140020">Matheus </persName>eas alicui vendere po<lb n="13" break="no" />terit nec ullius religionis homines nullo modo superinducet.
                        Pro his omnibus dederunt <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e140025" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetenses</orgName>
                        <persName key="d1e14409" xml:id="d1e140027">Matheo</persName> et uxori <lb n="14" /> ejus <persName key="d1e14415" xml:id="d1e140032">Adeline</persName> que hec omnia laudavit quinquaginta libras
                        proveniensis monete et concesserunt eis ut pro utroque in <lb n="15" /> obitu
                        suo tantum facerent quantum pro uno monacho. Hinc testes sunt : <persName key="d1e14421" xml:id="d1e140038">Josbertus abbas <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e140040" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14427" xml:id="d1e140043">Willelmus
                            prior</persName>, <lb n="16" />
                        <persName key="d1e14434" xml:id="d1e140047">Philippus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325251" xml:id="d1e140049" corresp="Corabœuf (Côte-d'Or, Arnay-le-Duc)">Curte Rabodi</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14440" xml:id="d1e140052">Bernardus de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e140054" corresp="Grignon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Grinione</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324623" xml:id="d1e140058" corresp="Eudes, archiprêtre de Touillon (1173-1200)">Odo
                            archipresbiter <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324370" xml:id="d1e140060" corresp="Touillon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Tullionis</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14446" xml:id="d1e140063">Andreas de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324438" xml:id="d1e140065" corresp="Courtangy (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                                <foreign>Cortenge</foreign>
                            </placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14452" xml:id="d1e140069">Robertus <lb n="17" /> major <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324370" xml:id="d1e140073" corresp="Touillon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Tullionis</placeName> et camerarius ducis</persName>. De laude
                        predicte <persName key="d1e14458" xml:id="d1e140077">Adeline</persName>
                        uxoris ejus testes sunt : <persName key="d1e14464" xml:id="d1e140080">Rainaudus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325251" xml:id="d1e140082" corresp="Corabœuf (Côte-d'Or, Arnay-le-Duc)">Curte
                                    <lb n="18" /> Rabodi</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14471" xml:id="d1e140087">Bernardus de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e140089" corresp="Grignon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Grinione</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324623" xml:id="d1e140093" corresp="Eudes, archiprêtre de Touillon (1173-1200)">Odo
                            archipresbiter</persName>, <persName key="d1e14477" xml:id="d1e140096">Hugo de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324998" xml:id="d1e140098" corresp="Baisse">
                                <foreign>Baisse</foreign>
                            </placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14483" xml:id="d1e140102">Robertus major
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324370" xml:id="d1e140104" corresp="Touillon (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Tullionis</placeName>
                        </persName>. <lb n="19" /> Actum est hoc anno ab incarnatione Domini .M°. C°.
                        <space />LXXX. <space />VI°.</p>
                
            </body>
